MOTION DOCKET

98-1097. First Bank of Marietta v. Roslovic & Partners, Inc.

Franklin App. Nos. 97APE09-1199 and 97APE09-1201. On amended motion for enforcement of judgment entry and for instructions. Motion denied.

Douglas, J., would grant. Pfeifer, J., would dismiss and award attorney fees against the movant.
